457
00:22:21.070 --> 00:22:22.930
should we ne'er have needof 'em?

458
00:22:22.930 --> 00:22:24.570
They're the most needlesscreatures living,

459
00:22:24.570 --> 00:22:26.500
should we ne'er have useof 'em,

460
00:22:26.500 --> 00:22:28.770
