O, what a precious comfort'tis,

468
00:22:53.370 --> 00:22:54.600
to have so many, likebrothers,

469
00:22:54.600 --> 00:22:58.370
commanding one another'sfortunes.

470
00:22:58.370 --> 00:23:02.270
Oh, joy's even made a wayere it can be born.

471
00:23:02.270 --> 00:23:05.130
