00:26:24.870 --> 00:26:29.300
Hoy-day, what a sweep ofvanity comes this way!

503
00:26:41.930 --> 00:26:43.530
They dance.

504
00:26:43.530 --> 00:26:45.270
They are mad women.

505
00:26:45.270 --> 00:26:48.030
Like madness is the gloryof this life.

506
00:26:48.030 --> 00:26:51.530
As this pomp shows to alittle oil and root.

507
00:26:51.530 --> 00:26:54.700
We make ourselves fools todisport ourselves;

508
00:26:54.700 --> 00:26:56.970
